        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.15</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.0.15</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Excludes shared Photos Library items from cleanup scans</li>
                    <li>Prevents shared iCloud Photos content from appearing in duplicate and similar-photo results</li>
                    <li>Improves deletion safety by only resolving user-owned Photos Library assets for cleanup actions</li>
                </ul>
