        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.13</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.0.13</h2>
                <p>
                    <strong>Important:</strong> After updating, macOS may ask Photiva for permission
                    to access your saved license in Keychain. Please choose <strong>Always Allow</strong>
                    and enter your Mac login password. If you choose <strong>Allow</strong>, macOS may ask more than once.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixes license activation persistence across app restarts</li>
                    <li>Restores the last selected Photos Library session on launch</li>
                    <li>Improves Photos Library duplicate deletion reliability and error reporting</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
